title: Keen refrence in JotJ?
content:
In Jill of the Jungle, there's a refrence to Keen appearing in a message box somewhere near level Two (judging by the screenshot at [url=http://www.3drealms.com/keenhistory/keenhistory3.html]3DRealms[/url])

My copy of Jill is Version 1.2, obviously a copy with the Keen refrence removed. Does anyone know which version(s) of Jill has got the message, or better yet, an actual copy of the version?
